</taxonomicName>
and its 
<typeStatus id="8B7EB2A9FFBEFFE46F2FFD3DFD1EA9B7" box="[607,651,672,693]" pageId="26" pageNumber="1539">type</typeStatus>
species were adequately described and illustrated in 
<bibRefCitation id="305471FAFFBEFFE46C48FD20FE7DA9D0" author="OPITZ W" box="[312,488,700,722]" pageId="26" pageNumber="1539" pagination="51 - 96" refId="ref26873" refString="OPITZ W. (1997): Classification, natural history, and evolution of the Epiphloeinae (Coleoptera: Cleridae). Part I. The genera of Epiphloeinae. - Insecta Mundi 11 (1): 51 - 96." type="journal article" year="1997">OPITZ (1997: 54)</bibRefCitation>
